quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not expanded for you your breast
  94,2,And set down from you your load
  94,3,Which galled your back
  94,4,And exalted for you your renown
  94,5,"Verily, with difficulty comes ease"
  94,6,"Verily, with difficulty comes ease"
  94,7,"So when you are at relieved, then still toil"
  94,8,And to your Lord turn all your yearning (or attention)